google_home.cancel_schedules_api.cancel_.message: Error 500: Internal server error - Failed to cancel the specified schedules.
Error 503: Service unavailable - The Google Home service is currently unable to process schedule cancellations.

Error 403: Forbidden - You do not have permission to cancel these schedules.
Error 429: Too many requests - You have exceeded the rate limit for cancelling schedules.
